PEOPLE
v.
BROWN S230134 Supreme Court of California March 15, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Two, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of People v. White (2017) 2 Cal.5th 349 , 212 Cal.Rptr.3d 376 , 386 P.3d 1172 . (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
